### ===================================
### 단축 URL API
### ===================================

### 5. URL 단축
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/util/shorturl
Content-Type: application/json
X-Naver-Client-Id: {{clientId}}
X-Naver-Client-Secret: {{clientSecret}}

{
  "url": "https://www.naver.com"
}

