### ===================================
### 지도 API
### ===================================

### 6. 주소 → 좌표 변환 (Geocoding)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/map/geocode?query=강남역
X-Naver-Client-Id: {{clientId}}
X-Naver-Client-Secret: {{clientSecret}}

###

### 7. 좌표 → 주소 변환 (Reverse Geocoding)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/map/reversegeocode?coords=127.027610,37.497942&output=json
X-Naver-Client-Id: {{clientId}}
X-Naver-Client-Secret: {{clientSecret}}

###

### 8. 경로 탐색 (길찾기)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/map/direction?start=127.027610,37.497942&goal=127.043065,37.514575
X-Naver-Client-Id: {{clientId}}
X-Naver-Client-Secret: {{clientSecret}}

###

### ===================================
### 음성 합성 API (TTS)
### ===================================

### 9. 텍스트를 음성으로 변환 (한국어 여성)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/voice/tts.bin
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
X-Naver-Client-Id: {{clientId}}
X-Naver-Client-Secret: {{clientSecret}}

speaker=nara&speed=0&text=안녕하세요

###

### 10. 텍스트를 음성으로 변환 (한국어 남성)
POST {{baseUrl}>/v1/voice/tts.bin
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
X-Naver-Client-Id: {{clientId}}
X-Naver-Client-Secret: {{clientSecret}}

speaker=jinho&speed=0&text=반갑습니다

###

